{"tid":1840313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推 所有局長去前線","createTime":"2020-01-24T19:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T19:41:59.000Z","uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2be4ca1f3614c320e90944cb15f3d933e66ad9","tid":1840313,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"2ee1bb1287fee2aa878a9cc08f99719f2a48ea67","tid":1840313,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"人神共憤! 醫護離開隔離房後做自我隔離時要扣AL !<br />\n<br />\n黑警殺人放火拎OT<br />\n醫護本命救人扣AL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvBczRW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvBczRW.jpg&h=0196f4ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d88a2fa4505c8e1df18d461adb985dc74f344d95","tid":1840313,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1bb1287fee2aa878a9cc08f99719f2a48ea67","tid":1840313,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"人神共憤! 醫護離開隔離房後做自我隔離時要扣AL !<br />\n<br />\n黑警殺人放火拎OT<br />\n醫護本命救人扣AL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvBczRW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvBczRW.jpg&h=0196f4ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:15:49.000Z","msg":"[封殺高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵大行動 ! 香港封關 ! 置頂 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838537\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838537</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請幫推 推上熱門</span></strong><br />\n祝各手足百毒不侵"},{"pid":"bbbf32053cf6dcf2fb6df702cd82cdc47f25009e","tid":1840313,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:18:26.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=419c6284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f36899f24c5d93eea335db25018fa0c83632ff5f","tid":1840313,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:19:06.000Z","msg":"局長捨得去慰問醫護人員未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378b79efb99c78db65a7bff6a644b3f9f97d5e0b","tid":1840313,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:19:57.000Z","msg":"林奠pk tang成日都探前線警<br />\n今次要探前線醫護啦"},{"pid":"5a96f54f6eb97b5748454b38eef822aa3a5f32ef","tid":1840313,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:20:24.000Z","msg":"[封殺高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵大行動 !  香港封關 ! 置頂 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838537</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6df82fbb3a43b92cacef5c66e1fc882b03eab98d","tid":1840313,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:20:49.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"459495527f159e87fe908c603f98b724315e2ef9","tid":1840313,"uid":172153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:21:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀 高層經驗夠<br />\n交翻個場比你"},{"pid":"70d2e08bc931216edb71af43da1662606499ba9b","tid":1840313,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1bb1287fee2aa878a9cc08f99719f2a48ea67","tid":1840313,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"人神共憤! 醫護離開隔離房後做自我隔離時要扣AL !<br />\n<br />\n黑警殺人放火拎OT<br />\n醫護本命救人扣AL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvBczRW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvBczRW.jpg&h=0196f4ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:41:59.000Z","msg":"呢個政府真係好撚仆街，封鐵咁低成本既野都唔做<br />\n醫護就要本條命出去<br />\n狗就食花生笑黑醫護"}]}